            <p>Let's say you have applied bold to a word in your topic. If the cursor is located on that word and you click this button, the content in the parent tag (e.g., &lt;p&gt;) will be selected. If you click the button yet again, the content in the &lt;body&gt; tag will be highlighted. And if you click the button once more, the content in the &lt;html&gt; tag will be selected.</p>
